author: Cleo Abram
description:
Have you ever wondered how an airplane engine works? 

First, air outside the plane is sucked in by a fan, where some of it gets squeezed through rotating blades. Then it’s mixed with fuel and lit on fire… but why? 

For more optimistic science and tech stories, subscribe! 

#shorts #airplane #jet #engine #science #technology
title: How Do Airplane Engines Work?
